asse sowie ihre intersektionalen Wechselwirkungen.  afunded by Backlisttransformation EOSC Future  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aThis eBook is made available Open Access under a CC BY 4.0 license: uhttps://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 06. Mrz 2024) 4aAbdellah Taïa. 4aFilm. 4aGender Studies. 4aGender. 4aGeschlecht. 4aIdentität. 4aIntersektionalität. 4aKlasse. 4aKulturwissenschaft. 4aLiteratur. 4aNadia El Fani. 4aPostkolonialismus. 4aRomanistik. 7aSOCIAL SCIENCE / Gender Studies.2bisacsh  aAbdellah Taïa.  aClass.  aCultural Studies.  aFilm.  aGender Studies.  aGender.  aIdentity.  aIntersectionality.  aLiterature.  aNadia El Fani.  aPostcolonialism.  aRomance Studies.2 aBacklisttransformation EOSC Futureefunder.4fnd4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/fnd08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Plus PP Package 2022 Part 2z978311076700108iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2022z9783110994810oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Literary, Cultural, Area Studies 2022z9783110993738oZDB-23-DKU08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe Gruyterttranscript Complete eBook Package 2022z9783111025094oZDB-23-TGP40uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/9783839462683?locatt=mode:legacyzOpen Access7040uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783839462683zOpen Access70423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783839462683/original  a978-3-11-076700-1 DG Plus PP Package 2022 Part 2b2022  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aZDB-23-DGGb2022  aZDB-23-DKUb2022  aZDB-23-GOA  aZDB-23-TGPb2022